OL,3,CMan denies knowing age of alleged
OL,4,Cvictim in Rhyl child exploitation trial
OL,6,FA child sexual exploitation trial has
OL,7,Fcontinued at Caernarfon Crown Court
OL,8,Fhearing from Jaswinder Singh, aged 61,
OL,9,Fwho denies charges of conspiracy to
OL,10,Ftraffic as part of what the
OL,11,Fprosecution alleges was a grooming
OL,12,Fgang.
OL,14,FThe court heard the defendant did not
OL,15,Fknow the age of the child when they
OL,16,Ftook them on a trip to London.
OL,18,FJaswinder Singh told the court that he
OL,19,Fwould never have taken her with him on
OL,20,Fa trip involving an overnight stay if
OL,21,Fhe'd known she was actually 15.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
