PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1782051073
OL,3,CMan denies knowing age of alleged
OL,4,Cvictim in Rhyl child exploitation trial
OL,6,FMr Singh had outlined to the court how
OL,7,Fhe met two of the teenage girls at the
OL,8,Fcentre of this case. On one occasion,
OL,9,Fwhen he met one of the teenage girls,
OL,10,FGirl B, during a trip from Rhyl to
OL,11,FManchester- he didn't discuss her age
OL,12,Fwith any of his co-defendants, nor
OL,13,Fraised any concerns about her age with
OL,14,Fthem.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
