PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1782051073
OL,3,CMan denies knowing age of alleged
OL,4,Cvictim in Rhyl child exploitation trial
OL,6,FJaswinder Singh, questioned by his
OL,7,Fdefence counsel Duncan Bould, told
OL,8,FCaernarfon Crown Court that he chatted
OL,9,Fwith Girl B on the journey to
OL,10,FManchester, accompanied by co-
OL,11,Fdefendants Mohammed Arshad and Ziah
OL,12,FBadshah. He told the court: "I said
OL,13,FI'm originally from London and I think
OL,14,Fshe said she has a good friend in
OL,15,FLondon and she wants to see her.''
OL,17,FAsked by Mr Bould: "Did you ask about
OL,18,Fher age?", Mr Singh replied: "no, no."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
