CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1782051073
OL,3,CMan denies knowing age of alleged
OL,4,Cvictim in Rhyl child exploitation trial
OL,6,FHe told the court that he knew his co-
OL,7,Fdefendants, Mustafa Iqbal, Ziah
OL,8,FBadshah and Mohammed Arshad as either
OL,9,Facquaintances or friends. He said that
OL,10,Fhe knew Mr Arshad from his cafe
OL,11,Fbusiness which was next door to the
OL,12,Fmobile phone shop where Mr Singh had
OL,13,Fworked and had developed a friendship
OL,14,Fwith Ziah Badshah.
OL,16,FAll 5 defendants in the trial have
OL,17,Fpleaded not guilty to all charges. The
OL,18,Ftrial continues next week.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/6
